high_descs: Move to the sink to the left
Pick up a knife from the sink
Move to the cabinet underneath the sink
Put the knife on the plate in the cabinet
Pick up the plate from the cabinet
Move to the sink ahead of you
Put the plate in the sink

high_descs: Turn to the left
Walk straight to the kitchen counter
Grab the knife on the counter
Turn to the left
Open the door to the under cabinet
Grab a cake pan and put the knife in the pan
Carry the items to the sink and put them in there
Turn to the left and face the sink.
Pick the yellow knife up off of the sink.
Move to the left and face the cabinet below the left sink.
Open the cabinet door from under the sink.
Remove the pan from the cabinet.
Move upwards to face the sink above the cabinet.
Place the pan in the sink
